253    public enum ChangeBitmask {
254        QUICK_BOLUS(2),
255        GENERAL(4),
256        REMINDER(8),
257        ALERT(16),
258        ALARM(32),
259        CGM_ALERT(64),
260
261
262        ;
263
264        private final int id;
265
266        ChangeBitmask(int id) {
267            this.id = id;
268        }
269
270        public int id() {
271            return id;
272        }
273
274        public static Set<ChangeBitmask> fromBitmask(int bitmask) {
275            Set<ChangeBitmask> set = new TreeSet<>();
276            for (ChangeBitmask i : values()) {
277                if ((bitmask & i.id()) != 0) {
278                    set.add(i);
279                }
280            }
281
282            return set;
283        }
284
285        public static int toBitmask(ChangeBitmask... items) {
286            int mask = 0;
287            for (ChangeBitmask i : items) {
288                mask += i.id();
289            }
290
291            return mask;
292        }
293    }
